		{
			description: [
				"Vanilla combat is just the start."
				""
				"§bSimply Swords§r adds new weapon types — Longswords, Claymores, War Scythes, Katanas and more. Each has unique reach, speed, and combo behaviour."
				""
				"§bBetter Combat§r overhauls attack animations and lets you dual-wield any two weapons. Put a weapon in your offhand and attack to combo with both."
				""
				"§6Relics§r and §6Artifacts§r give passive and active powers — found in loot or dropped by mobs."
			]
