			description: [
				"§6Artifacts§r are rare trinkets found in chests across the world — dungeons, mineshafts, strongholds, and structures."
				""
				"Unlike Relics, Artifacts are purely passive — equip them in a §bCurios§r slot and their effect activates automatically."
				""
				"Look for items like the §aFeral Claws§r (faster attack speed), §aCloud in a Bottle§r (double jump), or §aMimic Tooth Necklace§r (immunity to Mimic attacks)."
